trans-unit.source: Configuration Provider Extension: The name of the extension where the YAML-configuration lives. The path within the defined extension must be "/Configuration/ImageManipulation/CropVariants.yaml".

Localized Language file name without file extension: The file name without file extension where you want to overwrite or extend the automatic translation feature. E.g. "locallang" if the file is located at "EXT:<configurationProviderExtension>/Resources/Private/Language/locallang.xlf".
